						<h4 class="mb-5 forza-subtitle subtitle wow fadeInUp">
                          Grupo Dalt manages proprietary platform to ensure zero defect medication delivery and administration services to care institutions in Spain.
						</h4>
						<p>
                          Grupo Dalt is a Spain-based medication software and service provider with a mission to eliminate medication errors for dependent people. The platform is a combination of in-house developed software, adapted blistering and quality control machines for individual dosing, and just-in-time delivery logistics. Grupo Dalt currently operates out of seven different sites across various regions of Spain, serving several thousand patients in care institutions regularly.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
						</p>	
